&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;JOB TITLE: (i-Ready) Associate, Customer Success (UAG)&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What will you do?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an Associate, Customer Success (UAG), you will support the planning and execution of user engagement campaigns, events, and digital initiatives to enhance the BruHealth experience. You will work closely with internal teams, vendors, and stakeholders to coordinate campaigns, create engaging content, manage platform updates, analyze user feedback, and help deliver meaningful health and wellness programs for the community.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role reports to our Senior Associate, Customer Success (UAG), and is based in Brunei.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Your key responsibilities include:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;Plan and coordinate UAG-led campaigns and events (health walks, programme launches, pop-ups) across in-app and offline channels&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;Support content creation for campaigns - social media copy, in-app articles, push notifications - in both English and Malay&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;Design visual assets using Canva and assist with content scheduling across channels&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;Reach out to and onboard BruPoints vendors to the BruHealth Rewards Redemption Centre&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;Assist with platform configuration tasks (banners, rewards, articles, push notification) and perform quality checks&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;Collect and consolidate user feedback from events, campaigns, and social media&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;Track campaign performance metrics and support preparation of reports&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;Attend stakeholder and vendor meetings, prepare minutes, and maintain project trackers&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;Support coordination between UAG, Product, Technical, and Operations teams&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Qualifications and other skills requirements:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;Degree in Communications, Marketing, Business, IT, or a related field&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;Strong written and verbal communication in English; Malay is an advantage&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;Proficient in Microsoft Office and Canva&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;Organised, proactive, and comfortable working in a fast-paced team environment&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;Prior involvement in events, marketing, or digital campaigns is an advantage&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;JOB TITLE: (i-Ready) Associate, HR &amp;amp; Administration&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What will you do?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will support the day-to-day operations of the HR and administration function while gaining hands-on experience across HR operations, recruitment, employee engagement, office administration, executive support, and business support activities. Working closely with the senior HRBP and administration team, you will progressively take ownership of assigned responsibilities while contributing to the smooth running of daily operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This apprenticeship program provides structured on-the-job training and practical experience to help you build a strong foundation for a career in HR and administration.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role reports to our senior HRBP and is based in Brunei.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Your key responsibilities include:&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;1. HR Administration &amp;amp; Operations&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain and update employee records, databases, and personnel files.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support onboarding and offboarding activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare employment-related documentation and correspondence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure the accuracy and confidentiality of employee information.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with employee records management and HR process documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support continuous improvements to HR and administrative processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide administrative support across the employee lifecycle.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;2.&amp;nbsp;Recruitment &amp;amp; Talent Acquisition&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support job postings across recruitment platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Screen resumes and coordinate interview schedules.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support candidate communications and recruitment administration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with onboarding arrangements for new hires.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Administration &amp;amp; Employee Engagement&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
