&lt;li&gt;Support day-to-day office administration activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in coordinating employee engagement initiatives, team events, and company celebrations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support internal communications and culture-building initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shadow and support business travel arrangements, including accommodation, transportation, and visitor logistics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with internal stakeholders, travel teams, and employees on travel-related administrative arrangements when required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with other administrative and operational tasks as assigned.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
