&lt;li&gt;Support third-party du

&lt;h3&gt;In Brief:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;EVYD Technology is seeking a proactive, commercially driven, and resourceful Senior Associate, Business Development to join our Brunei team. This role is suited for an individual with experience in business development, account management, partnerships, consulting, or related functions, with proven experience in customer relationship and account management. Exposure to healthcare, information technology (IT), artificial intelligence (AI), digital transformation, or related industries will be highly advantageous. The successful candidate should possess a strong understanding of Brunei’s healthcare ecosystem, including government healthcare institutions, private healthcare providers, digital health initiatives, and the evolving AI and technology landscape.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;As part of this role, you will represent EVYD locally, build and strengthen strategic stakeholder relationships, identify new business opportunities, and support the growth of EVYD’s healthcare AI and digital health solutions in Brunei.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role reports to our Senior Manager, Business Development, and will be based in Brunei Darussalam.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Your key responsibilities include:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1.&amp;nbsp;Business Development &amp;amp; Opportunity Identification&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct market research and monitor healthcare, AI, digital transformation, and technology trends relevant to Brunei and the wider region.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively identify business opportunities, strategic initiatives, and potential projects aligned with EVYD’s healthcare AI, digital health, and enterprise technology solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain a strong pipeline of commercial opportunities, partnerships, and customer engagements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify customer pain points, operational challenges, and transformation priorities that can be addressed through EVYD’s solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2.&amp;nbsp;Customer &amp;amp; Stakeholder Engagement&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1737uy3&quot; data-start=&quot;2260&quot; data-end=&quot;2377&quot;&gt;Build and maintain strong relationships with stakeholders across Brunei’s healthcare and digital ecosystem, including government agencies, hospitals, clinics, healthcare providers, insurers, IT partners, and innovation ecosystem stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1737uy3&quot; data-start=&quot;2260&quot; data-end=&quot;2377&quot;&gt;Serve as a trusted point of contact for strategic customers, partners, and key accounts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1737uy3&quot; data-start=&quot;2260&quot; data-end=&quot;2377&quot;&gt;Conduct regular engagement sessions with customers to understand business priorities, operational challenges, digital transformation initiatives, and AI adoption opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1737uy3&quot; data-start=&quot;2260&quot; data-end=&quot;2377&quot;&gt;Represent EVYD at meetings, ecosystem engagements, industry events, and strategic discussions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3.&amp;nbsp;Solution Development &amp;amp; Internal Collaboration&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain close collaboration with product, AI, technical, project delivery, and leadership teams to stay aligned on product capabilities, technology developments, and solution roadmaps.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gather business and technical requirements and translate customer needs into solution opportunities, proposals, or project scopes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with internal teams to develop relevant healthcare AI and digital transformation solutions for target customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support solution positioning, value proposition development, and go-to-market initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
